ghasher: ghasher (GUI hasher for GTK+ 2)
ghasher:
ghasher: ghasher can easily show the MD5 sum (or md2, md4, sha1, sha,
ghasher: ripemd160, dss1) of a file. Motivation for this utility was that
ghasher: users shouldn't need to open a command line for checking the MD5
ghasher: sum of files they download.
ghasher:
ghasher: http://asgaard.homelinux.org/code/ghasher/
